# Schedule definitions for thorn WeakLibInterpTest
#
# One startup routine so the smoke object is referenced by the scheduler and
# therefore pulled out of the thorn archive into the final link — a thorn
# object nothing references would never exercise the wli_lib link at all.

SCHEDULE WeakLibInterpTest_Smoke AT startup
{
  LANG: C
} "Call one WeakLibInterp _Point per kernel family on tiny synthetic tables"
